{"name": "raydiumsdk", "metadata": {"name": "raydiumsdk", "version": "0.3.0", "classifiers": ["Environment :: Console", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Topic :: Terminals", "Topic :: Text Processing", "Topic :: Utilities"], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["solana", "solders"], "summary": "Solana Python API", "upload_time": 1733493891}, "documentation": ["# raydium\r\n\r\nPython library to trade on Raydium.\r\n\r\n### Setting up\r\n\r\nbash\r\n```\r\nexport PRIVATE_KEY=base_58_private_key\r\nexport RPC_URL=rpc_url\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\ncmd\r\n```\r\nset PRIVATE_KEY=base_58_private_key\r\nset RPC_URL=rpc_url\r\n```\r\n\r\n### FAQS\r\n\r\n**What format should my private key be in?** \r\n\r\nThe private key should be in the base58 string format, not bytes. \r\n\r\n**Why are my transactions being dropped?** \r\n\r\nYou get what you pay for. Don't use the main-net RPC, just spend the money for Helius or Quick Node.\r\n\r\n**How do I change the fee?** \r\n\r\nModify the UNIT_BUDGET and UNIT_PRICE in the config.py. \r\n\r\n**Why is this failing for USDC pairs?** \r\n\r\nThis code only works for SOL pairs. \r\n\r\n**Why are there \"no pool keys found\"?** \r\n\r\nIF YOU ARE USING A FREE TIER RPC, THIS REPO WILL NOT WORK FOR YOU. FREE TIER RPCS DO NOT ALLOW GET_ACCOUNT_INFO_PARSED().\r\n\r\n### Examples\r\n\r\n```\r\nfrom raydium import buy\r\nfrom utils import get_pair_address\r\n\r\n# Buy Example\r\ntoken_address = \"7GCihgDB8fe6KNjn2MYtkzZcRjQy3t9GHdC8uHYmW2hr\" # POPCAT\r\npair_address = get_pair_address(token_address)\r\nsol_in = .1\r\nslippage = 5\r\nbuy(pair_address, sol_in, slippage)\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\nfrom raydium import sell\r\nfrom utils import get_pair_address\r\n\r\n# Sell Example\r\ntoken_address = \"7GCihgDB8fe6KNjn2MYtkzZcRjQy3t9GHdC8uHYmW2hr\" # POPCAT\r\npair_address = get_pair_address(token_address)\r\npercentage = 100\r\nslippage = 5\r\nsell(pair_address, percentage, slippage)\r\n```\r\n"], "modules": [{"name": "raydium.example_sell", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "raydium.example_sell.token_address", "type": null, "documentation": ["POPCAT"]}, {"name": "raydium.example_sell.pair_address", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "raydium.example_sell.percentage", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "raydium.example_sell.slippage", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "raydium.example_buy", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "raydium.example_buy.token_address", "type": null, "documentation": ["POPCAT"]}, {"name": "raydium.example_buy.pair_address", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "raydium.example_buy.sol_in", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "raydium.example_buy.slippage", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "raydium.constants", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "raydium.constants.WSOL", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "raydium.constants.RAY_V4", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "raydium.constants.RAY_AUTHORITY_V4", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "raydium.constants.OPEN_BOOK_PROGRAM", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "raydium.constants.TOKEN_PROGRAM_ID", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "raydium.constants.SOL", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "raydium.constants.SOL_DECIMAL", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "raydium", "documentation": ["Raydium Library packages."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "raydium.config", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "raydium.config.PRIV_KEY", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "raydium.config.RPC", "type": null, "documentatio